messages.messageBody:
So I'm going to unsub soon. Hey, it is only two months away, and we are
starting to pack, tomorrow we go to the appliance store and figure out those
needs, we have to sell the house...DEEP BREATH!!!!BUT, I have tons of
different books and there is no way we can get them to Israel. I won't be
able to fit them on the shelves!!!! Here are some I think some of you may
be interested in. LMK if you want them (off list) and ask away if you have a
specific want. I may have your book!!!!

S/h not included.
A Mathematical Mystery Tour: except for the dust jacket this is in great
shape. $10
Bet you Can't...Cover is messed up $2
The Practice of Poetry Dust jacket messed up. Otherwise fine. $5
I've also got History Plus and Let the Authors Speak, in good condition, $5
each.
I

be well,
Rachel Ann
